HEADWORD: Archæozoic
<hw>Ar`ch⟦ae⟧*o*zo"ic</hw></mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>'archai^os</grk> ancient +
<grk>zw^,on</grk> animal.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Like or
belonging to the earliest forms of animal life.</def>⟦br⟧
